// ...
const navigate = useNavigate();
```

`navigate` is declared but never used in the component — all navigation is handled by the `onPostClick` prop callback passed in from `ExplorePage`. This will trigger a React/ESLint warning and, more importantly, wastes the hook call on every render. Remove both lines:

```jsx
// Remove:
import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom";
// Remove:
const navigate = useNavigate();
```

